BBK01.SU0304: Money market rates / EONIA / Monthly average

General: Euro OverNight Index Average: weighted average overnight rate for interbank operations calculated by the European Central Bank since 4 January 1999 on the basis of real turnover according to the act/360 method and published via Reuters. Monthly averages are Bundesbank calculations. Data become fee liable from 1 January 2014 and therefore will be published with the delay of one working day.
